e-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2c0b6e8f-f8c1-4fe9-bbd1-fc0a4a9d6f93\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-33f6fc5b-7640-43af-9784-2440689f7671\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5dd2556e-bdb0-4e9e-9b13-cdd1da256627\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄에서 가장 단가를 죄우하는 것이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-de1db5fc-eb94-49b6-ae7d-6deb9f0dbfc2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-96c6ad7b-aee1-4e6f-a1f1-d233ab1188ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-69c4e719-904a-4b35-9d96-9482b97a8ec3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de88d9f8-b56d-4d74-8831-5201bdf5eddc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 종이는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-443ccf8a-ca5f-453f-ad4c-6829162bcf86\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a6737813-9f33-46b5-a27c-834e764b01ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>1R이라는 단위</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92db4c5c-7ea4-4633-9d14-8024b806a613\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fd1cc437-4242-445c-bd18-15e6d6a5e2e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c20504f-ff53-4d60-a3b7-9019ac8d4a62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">통용되고 또한 인쇄비</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ad20e56c-05f3-4dd9-a1e3-209127ed71eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fccf88d0-021e-41e6-8281-8af9eb24e050\" style=\"color:#555555;\">책정이 R(REAM or ROUND)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e86315c5-ca5c-4076-abe3-9abb3181b3cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c97183ec-546d-4fcc-9a1c-86eb866549e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단위로 계산됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d9bddf5d-93ac-4319-a8b9-0240c324d73e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f17adc94-ad49-4c3c-bae0-84757b75bd16\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0baff6b4-5292-45fd-b5d2-e9f3237c8666\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38d42f70-51cf-4d41-bbd0-d44c5bdf0124\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇게 때문에 전단의 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1aa4d150-0957-4c82-99d7-953a5a4ec656\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34367f6d-16f6-4e13-8fe4-ce0c6004d1f2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">A4 4,000장이 기본이라서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b9964381-28b0-4846-ac3a-43b4b0598c08\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-32b950a7-9942-46d0-9974-c388fd8da6be\" style=\"color:#555555;\">4,000장을 인쇄하나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p